Sentencas: NiO-YSZ nano-composite thin film mixed ionic electronic conducting (MIEC) electrode was prepared by co-sputtering technique.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: Pure nickel target and YSZ target were used for DC and RF sputtering, respectively.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: XRD analysis was carried out for both as deposited samples and annealed samples.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: Annealing was conducted at 800 degrees C for 2 h. Fully crystallized structure was achieved from annealed samples.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: Investigations of composition ratio versus deposition power and surface morphology were performed using FESEM and EDX.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: The NiO-YSZ nano-composite thin film was used as an anode on one side of an YSZ electrolyte and porous Pt was used as a cathode on the other side of an electrolyte to form solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: The cell test was carried out at 600 degrees C for 10 h with dry H-2 and air.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: The open circuit voltage was measured 1.016 V and reduced 0.94 V after 10 h experiments.
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique

Sentencas: The maximum power density was measured 23.3 mW/cm(2) and reduced 19.8 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Multi-component nano-composite electrode for SOFCS via thin film technique
